":"August 19, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Jabir reported: A man came to the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, saying, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, what are the two inevitabilities?\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cWhoever dies without associating anything with Allah will enter Paradise, and whoever dies associating anything with Allah will enter Hellfire.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":2963,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/04\/19\/dies-shirk-idolatry-ploytheism-nar\/","url_meta":{"origin":268,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Shirk: Whoever dies associating idols with Allah","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 19, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Mas'ud reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever dies while associating partners with Allah will enter Hellfire.\u201d And I said in his presence, \u201cWhoever dies without associating partners with Allah will enter Paradise.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 1181,\u00a0S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 92 Grade: Muttafaqun Alayhi\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":2016,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/02\/28\/hereafter-faith-eventually-jannah\/","url_meta":{"origin":268,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Akhirah: Whoever has faith eventually enters Paradise","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"February 28, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Dharr reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cGabriel, upon him be peace, came to me to give the good news that anyone from my nation who dies without associating partners with Allah will eventually enter Paradise.\u201d I said, \u201cEven if he commits adultery\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":3239,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/05\/19\/isa-abd-allah-ruh-maryam\/","url_meta":{"origin":268,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Eisa: Whoever testifies that Jesus is the servant of Allah","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 19, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"'Ubadah ibn al-Samit reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever testifies that there is no God but Allah alone without any partners, that Muhammad is His servant and His Messenger, that Jesus is the servant of Allah and His Messenger, His word which He\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":35318,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/02\/27\/never-barred-jannah\/","url_meta":{"origin":268,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Tawhid: Sincere Muslims never barred from Paradise","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"February 27, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cI bear witness there is no God but Allah and I am the Messenger of Allah. A servant who meets Allah testifying to these two statements, without any doubt, will not be barred from Paradise.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":35331,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/02\/27\/tawheed-jannah\/","url_meta":{"origin":268,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Tawhid: Glad tidings of Paradise for professing monotheism","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"February 27, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said to him, \u201cO Abu Huraira, go forth and whomever you meet who testifies with conviction in his heart that there is no God but Allah, give him the glad tidings of Paradise.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 31\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/268","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/3712"}],"replies":[{"embedda